'''Tafriqt ugafa''' neɣ '''Tamazɣa''' (Tafarka - Ugafa) d tamnaṭ d yezgan eg usamer n [[Tafriqt|Tefriqt]] : [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|Tamurt n leqbayel]], [[Dzayer]], [[Maṣer]], [[Libya]], [[Merruk]], [[Tunes]], [[Kanaries]], atg. 

== Igduden ==
Deg Ugafa n Tefriqt, imezdaɣen ineṣliyen neɣ imezdaɣen-imenza d [[Imaziɣen]], d nitni ay d amur ameqran deg yimezdaɣen n [[Tamazɣa|Tmazɣa]], xas ma yella aṭas deg-sen ass-a i la ttmeslayen [[taɛrabt]] ukk d/neɣ d Tafransist. Imaziɣen egan-ed tilas i wakal d ameqran, yewwet-ed seg wemda n [[Siwa]], deg Utaram (West) n [[Maṣer]] aramma d Targa Zewwaɣen (tazeggart) d [[Muritanya]], af (ɣef) yiri n ugaraw Atlasi neɣ adrar n watlas. 

Akal n Yimaziɣen, seg wakken meqqer aramma ay yewweḍ ɣer wul (tlemmast) n Tefriqt. D [[Imuhaɣ]] neɣ Imucaɣ ay d agdud n Yimaziɣen ay lin (yesɛan) akal meqqren akk gar igduden imaziɣen wiyyaḍ, xas akken ur ttuggtan ara. Akal-nsen d [[Aneɛruf]] (Idurar n Tasili, n Ayer di [[Niger]], atg.).

